Description of 1,108 older patients referred by their physician to the 
"Geriatric Frailty Clinic (G.F.C) for Assessment of Frailty and Prevention of 
Disability" at the gerontopole.

Tavassoli N(1), Guyonnet S, Abellan Van Kan G, Sourdet S, Krams T, Soto ME, 
Subra J, Chicoulaa B, Ghisolfi A, Balardy L, Cestac P, Rolland Y, Andrieu S, 
